{"id":232936104,"title":"釜山海雲臺海水浴場(해운대해수욕장)","content":"海雲臺海水浴場(해운대해수욕장)為釜山目前最具知名度的海水浴場，很多人想到釜山就會想到海雲臺，幾乎快成為釜山觀光的代名詞。\n\n千年前新羅著名學者崔致遠(최치원)來到這裡，被這邊的美景吸引，於是用自己的字命名為「海雲」，這就是海雲臺的由來。千年前的海雲臺怎樣不得而知，不過現在的海雲臺景觀確實相當美麗。\n\n跟廣安里海水浴場一樣，搭地鐵就可以抵達海雲臺海水浴場附近，釜山地鐵2號線海雲臺站3或5號出口出來沿龜南路直走就到達，交通便利路線簡單，難怪總是湧入非常多人。\n\n來海雲臺若時間夠的話，Xavier建議再到旁邊的冬柏島海岸散步路(동백섬해안산책로)走走，很多人嫌走的路遠放棄，偏偏冬柏島海岸散步路的海景絕美，沒來這邊看看真的可惜了。\n\n\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/78wjsLH.jpg\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/CcOsvG7.jpg\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/DIE9Kb4.jpg\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/uWsiQjA.jpg\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/vB9NzSC.jpg\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/WBOc1ho.jpg\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/qISHpp9.jpg\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/r37bI92.jpg\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/TxGtpgv.jpg\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/XG7OxM7.jpg\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/DLasjQT.jpg\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/6N0oORZ.jpg\n\n \n更多照片和介紹: https://peavy.pixnet.net/blog/post/49103860","excerpt":"海雲臺海水浴場（해운대해수욕장）為釜山目前最具知名度的海水浴場，很多人想到釜山就會想到海雲臺，幾乎快成為釜山觀光的代名詞。千年前新羅著名學者崔致遠（최치원）來到這裡，被這邊的美景吸引，於是用自己的字命","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"a255fb97-4199-4bd0-9b28-1ec2c0d2f382","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-22T03:30:29.115Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-22T03:30:29.115Z","commentCount":1,"likeCount":12,"tags":[],"topics":["釜山","自由行","遊記","韓國","旅遊"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"旅遊","forumAlias":"travel","school":"Xavier","department":"sanchers","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":12}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/78wjsLH.jpg"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/CcOsvG7.jpg"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/DIE9Kb4.jpg"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/uWsiQjA.jpg"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/vB9NzSC.jpg"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/WBOc1ho.jpg"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/qISHpp9.jpg"},{"url":